description:
Julius (Terry Crews) decides the family is celebrating Kwanzaa instead of Christmas after he doesn’t get his bonus at work… and things fall apart fast. Tonya (Imani Hakim) starts stealing gifts, Drew (Tequan Richmond) suddenly swears off white people, and Chris (Tyler James Williams) isn’t even home to celebrate. Season 3 Episode 10: Everybody Hates Kwanzaa.
